---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="60 Seconds — Agnès Mercadé">
  <div class="secs-page">

    <h1 class="secs-title">60 seconds</h1>

    <div class="secs-video">
      <iframe
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/stwBYIIKDeM"
        title="60 seconds"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
      ></iframe>
    </div>

    <div class="secs-desc">
      <p data-i18n="secs.p1">60 seconds is a 60-second audiovisual piece created during my BA in Photography in London, where the only requirement was its duration.</p>
      <p data-i18n="secs.p2">A rainy day on the Costa Brava unfolds through sound, rhythm, and shifting images, captured from the interior of my home. Looking out at the landscape, I recorded small fragments of the world outside as it changed with the rain, creating a quiet, continuous flow of images.</p>
      <p data-i18n="secs.p3">The piece is built from simple, observational clips, where rain, movement, and ambient sound merge into a calm, immersive atmosphere. Each cut follows the rhythm of the audio, shaping a slow visual cadence.</p>
      <p data-i18n="secs.p4">Rather than documenting a specific event, the work reflects a personal moment of stillness and attention. The repetition of sound and image creates a suspended sense of time, where the everyday becomes almost meditative.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .secs-page {
    padding: calc(var(--nav-height) + 3rem) 13vw 6rem;
    max-width: var(--site-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .secs-title {
    font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 120px);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ── Video: full content width, responsive 16:9 ── */
  .secs-video {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 0 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 56.25%;
    height: 0;
  }

  .secs-video iframe {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: none;
  }

  /* ── Description: centered, readable width ── */
  .secs-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-align: justify;
  }

  .secs-desc p + p { margin-top: 1rem; }

</style>
